trans-unit.source: QCategory3DAxis provides an axis that can be given labels. The axis is divided into equal-sized categories based on the data window size defined by setting the axis range.
trans-unit.target: QCategory3DAxis提供了一个可以被赋予标签的轴。根据设置轴范围所定义的数据窗口大小,该轴被分成大小相等的类别。

trans-unit.source: QCborArray is very similar to QVariantList and QJsonArray and its API is almost identical to those two classes. It can also be converted to and from those two, though there may be loss of information in some conversions.
trans-unit.target: QCborArray与QVariantList和QJsonArray非常相似，其API与这两个类几乎相同。尽管在某些转换中可能会丢失信息，但它也可以在这两个之间来回转换。

trans-unit.source: QCborMap can also be converted to and from QVariantMap and QJsonObject. However, when performing the conversion, any non-string keys will be stringified using a one-way method that the conversion back to QCborMap will not undo.
trans-unit.target: QCborMap也可以与QVariantMap和QJsonObject相互转换。但是，在执行转换时，将使用单向方法对任何非字符串键进行字符串化，这样返回QCborMap的转换将不会撤消。

trans-unit.source: QCborMap is not sorted, because of that, searching for keys has linear complexity (O(n)). QCborMap actually keeps the elements in the order that they were inserted, which means that it is possible to make sorted QCborMaps by carefully inserting elements in sorted order. CBOR does not require sorting, but recommends it.
trans-unit.target: QCborMap是没有排序的,因为这样,搜索键的复杂性是线性的(O(n))。QCborMap实际上保持了元素的插入顺序,这意味着可以通过小心翼翼地按排序顺序插入元素来制作排序的QCborMaps。CBOR不需要排序,但推荐使用排序。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamReader is capable of detecting corrupt input on its own. The library it uses has been extensively tested against invalid input of any kind and is quite able to report errors. If any is detected, QCborStreamReader will set lastError() to a value besides QCborError::NoError, indicating which situation was detected.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamReader能够自行检测损坏的输入。它使用的库已经针对各种无效输入进行了广泛的测试，并且能够报告错误。如果检测到任何情况，QCborStreamReader会将lastError（）设置为QCborError :: NoError以外的值，指示检测到哪种情况。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamReader provides a StAX-like API, similar to that of QXmlStreamReader. Using it requires a bit of knowledge of CBOR encoding. For a simpler API, see QCborValue and especially the decoding function QCborValue::fromCbor().
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamReader提供类似于StAX的API，类似于QXmlStreamReader。使用它需要对CBOR编码有一点了解。有关更简单的API，请参见QCborValue，尤其是解码函数QCborValue :: fromCbor（）。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter does not take ownership of
QCborStreamWriter has no buffering, so every append() call will result in one or more calls to the device's write() method.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter没有缓冲，因此每个append（）调用都会导致对设备的write（）方法的一个或多个调用。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter provides a StAX-like API, similar to that of QXmlStreamWriter. It is rather low-level and requires a bit of knowledge of CBOR encoding. For a simpler API, see QCborValue and especially the encoding function QCborValue::toCbor().
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter提供类似于StAX的API，类似于QXmlStreamWriter。它相当底层，需要一些CBOR编码知识。有关更简单的API，请参见QCborValue，尤其是编码函数QCborValue :: toCbor（）。

trans-unit.source: QCborStreamWriter supports all CBOR features required to create canonical and strict streams. It implements almost all of the features specified in RFC 7049.
trans-unit.target: QCborStreamWriter支持创建规范和严格流所需的所有CBOR功能。它实现了RFC 7049中指定的几乎所有功能。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue can also be of the undefined type, which represents a value of "undefined". In fact, that is what the QCborValue default constructor creates.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue也可以是undefined类型,它代表一个 "undefined "的值。事实上,这就是QCborValue默认构造函数所创建的。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue can contain a value of "null", which is not of any specific type. It resembles the C++ std::nullptr_t type, whose only possible value is nullptr. QCborValue has a constructor taking such a type and creates a null QCborValue.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue可以包含“ null”值，该值不是任何特定类型。它类似于C ++ std::nullptr_t 类型，其唯一可能的值为 nullptr 。QCborValue具有采用这种类型的构造函数，并创建一个空QCborValue。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue has support for certain extended types in the API, like URL (with QUrl) and UUID (with QUuid). Other extended types not supported in the API are represented by a QCborValue of Tag type. The tag can later be retrieved by tag() and the tagged value using taggedValue().
trans-unit.target: QCborValue支持API中的某些扩展类型，例如URL（带有QUrl）和UUID（带有QUuid）。API中不支持的其他扩展类型由Tag类型的QCborValue表示。以后可以通过标签（）和使用aggedValue（）的标签值来检索标签。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue object into this one and frees the resources of this one.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue对象进入这个对象,并释放这个对象的资源。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue objects with undefined values are also different from invalid QCborValue objects. The API will not create invalid QCborValues, but they may exist as a result of a parsing error.
trans-unit.target: 具有未定义值的QCborValue对象也不同于无效的QCborValue对象。API不会创建无效的QCborValues,但它们可能因为解析错误而存在。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue supports all CBOR features required to create canonical and strict streams. It implements almost all of the features specified in RFC 7049.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue支持创建规范流和严格流所需的所有CBOR功能。它实现了RFC 7049中指定的几乎所有功能。

trans-unit.source: QCborValue will always convert half- and single-precision floating point values in the CBOR stream to double-precision. The toCbor() function can take a parameter indicating to recreate them.
trans-unit.target: QCborValue将始终将CBOR流中的半精度和单精度浮点值转换为双精度。所述toCbor（）函数可以取指示重新创建它们的参数。

trans-unit.source: QChar also provides direction(), which indicates the "natural" writing direction of this character. The joiningType() function indicates how the character joins with it's neighbors (needed mostly for Arabic or Syriac) and finally hasMirrored(), which indicates whether the character needs to be mirrored when it is printed in it's "unnatural" writing direction.
trans-unit.target: QChar还提供了direction（），它指示此字符的“自然”书写方向。该joiningType（）函数表示角色与它的邻国（主要是需要阿拉伯语或叙利亚）如何连接和最后hasMirrored（），这表示当它在它的“不自然”书写方向被打印到镜像角色的需求。

trans-unit.source: QChar provides a full complement of testing/classification functions, converting to and from other formats, converting from composed to decomposed Unicode, and trying to compare and case-convert if you ask it to.
trans-unit.target: QChar提供了一个完整的测试/分类功能,转换到其他格式和从其他格式转换,从组成的Unicode转换到分解的Unicode,并尝试比较和大小写转换,如果你要求它这样做。

trans-unit.source: QChar provides constructors and cast operators that make it easy to convert to and from traditional 8-bit chars. If you defined QT_NO_CAST_FROM_ASCII and QT_NO_CAST_TO_ASCII, as explained in the QString documentation, you will need to explicitly call fromLatin1(), or use QLatin1Char, to construct a QChar from an 8-bit char, and you will need to call toLatin1() to get the 8-bit value back.
trans-unit.target: QChar提供了构造函数和强制转换运算符，可轻松地与传统的8位 char 进行相互转换。如果按照QString文档中的说明定义了 QT_NO_CAST_FROM_ASCII 和 QT_NO_CAST_TO_ASCII ，则需要显式调用fromLatin1（）或使用QLatin1Char从8位 char 构造QChar ，并且需要调用toLatin1（）来获取返回8位值。

trans-unit.source: QChart is a QGraphicsWidget that you can show in a QGraphicsScene. It manages the graphical representation of different types of series and other chart related objects like legend and axes. To simply show a chart in a layout, the convenience class QChartView can be used instead of QChart. In addition, line, spline, area, and scatter series can be presented as polar charts by using the QPolarChart class.
trans-unit.target: QChart是一个QGraphicsWidget，可以在QGraphicsScene中显示。它管理不同类型系列和其他与图表相关的对象（如图例和轴）的图形表示。为了仅在布局中显示图表，可以使用便利类QChartView代替QChart。另外，通过使用QPolarChart类，可以将折线，样条曲线，面积和散布序列表示为极坐标图。

trans-unit.source: QClipAnimator is a component providing simple animation playback capabilities. More...
trans-unit.target: QClipAnimator是提供简单动画播放功能的组件。更多的...

trans-unit.source: QClipAnimator is a component providing simple animation playback capabilities. More...
trans-unit.target: QClipAnimator是提供简单动画播放功能的组件。更多的...

trans-unit.source: QClipboard features some convenience functions to access common data types: setText() allows the exchange of Unicode text and setPixmap() and setImage() allows the exchange of QPixmaps and QImages between applications. The setMimeData() function is the ultimate in flexibility: it allows you to add any QMimeData into the clipboard. There are corresponding getters for each of these, e.g. text(), image() and pixmap(). You can clear the clipboard by calling clear().
trans-unit.target: QClipboard具有一些访问常用数据类型的便利功能：setText（）允许交换Unicode文本和setPixmap（）和setImage（）允许在应用程序之间交换QPixmaps和QImages。该setMimeData（）函数是灵活性的终极：它可以让你任意添加QMimeData到剪贴板。这些中的每一个都有对应的吸气剂，例如text（），image（）和pixmap（）。您可以通过调用clear（）来清除剪贴板。

trans-unit.source: QClipboard supports the same data types that QDrag does, and uses similar mechanisms. For advanced clipboard usage read Drag and Drop.
trans-unit.target: QClipboard支持相同的数据类型QDrag做，并采用类似的机制。有关剪贴板的高级用法，请阅读拖放。

trans-unit.source: QCollator is initialized with a QLocale and an optional collation strategy. It tries to initialize the collator with the specified values. The collator can then be used to compare and sort strings in a locale dependent fashion.
trans-unit.target: 使用QLocale和可选的排序规则策略初始化QCollat​​or。它尝试使用指定的值初始化整理程序。然后可以使用整理器以与语言环境相关的方式对字符串进行比较和排序。

trans-unit.source: QColor also support alpha-blended outlining and filling. The alpha channel of a color specifies the transparency effect, 0 represents a fully transparent color, while 255 represents a fully opaque color. For example:
trans-unit.target: QColor还支持alpha混合勾画和填充。颜色的alpha通道指定了透明度效果,0代表完全透明的颜色,而255代表完全不透明的颜色。例如

trans-unit.source: QColor is platform and device independent. The QColormap class maps the color to the hardware.
trans-unit.target: QColor是平台和设备独立的。该QColormap类映射颜色到硬件。

trans-unit.source: QColor supports floating point precision and provides floating point versions of all the color components functions, e.g. getRgbF(), hueF() and fromCmykF(). Note that since the components are stored using 16-bit integers, there might be minor deviations between the values set using, for example, setRgbF() and the values returned by the getRgbF() function due to rounding.
trans-unit.target: QColor支持浮点精度，并提供所有颜色组件功能的浮点版本，例如getRgbF（），hueF（）和fromCmykF（）。请注意，由于使用16位整数存储组件，因此，由于舍入，在使用setRgbF（）设置的值与getRgbF（）函数返回的值之间可能会有微小的偏差。

trans-unit.source: QColorSpace can also represent color spaces defined by ICC profiles or embedded in images, that do not otherwise fit the predefined color spaces.
trans-unit.target: QColorSpace也可以表示由ICC配置文件定义的颜色空间或嵌入图像中的颜色空间,否则不适合预定义的颜色空间。

trans-unit.source: QColorSpace provides access to creating several predefined color spaces and can generate QColorTransforms for converting colors from one color space to another.
trans-unit.target: QColorSpace提供了创建多个预定义色彩空间的访问权限,并且可以生成QColorTransform,用于将颜色从一个色彩空间转换到另一个色彩空间。

trans-unit.source: QColorTransform is an instantiation of a transformation between color spaces. It can be applied on color and pixels to convert them from one color space to another.
trans-unit.target: QColorTransform是颜色空间之间转换的一个实例。它可以应用在颜色和像素上,将它们从一个颜色空间转换到另一个颜色空间。

trans-unit.source: QColumnView displays a model in a number of QListViews, one for each hierarchy in the tree. This is sometimes referred to as a cascading list.
trans-unit.target: QColumnView在多个QListViews中显示一个模型,树中的每个层次结构都有一个。这有时被称为层叠列表。

trans-unit.source: QColumnView implements the interfaces defined by the QAbstractItemView class to allow it to display data provided by models derived from the QAbstractItemModel class.
trans-unit.target: QColumnView实现了由QAbstractItemView类定义的接口，以使其能够显示从QAbstractItemModel类派生的模型提供的数据。

trans-unit.source: QComboBox uses the model/view framework for its popup list and to store its items. By default a QStandardItemModel stores the items and a QListView subclass displays the popuplist. You can access the model and view directly (with model() and view()), but QComboBox also provides functions to set and get item data (e.g., setItemData() and itemText()). You can also set a new model and view (with setModel() and setView()). For the text and icon in the combobox label, the data in the model that has the Qt::DisplayRole and Qt::DecorationRole is used. Note that you cannot alter the SelectionMode of the view(), e.g., by using setSelectionMode().
trans-unit.target: QComboBox使用模型/视图框架为其弹出列表并存储其项目。默认情况下，QStandardItemModel存储项目，而QListView子类显示弹出列表。您可以直接访问模型和视图（使用模型（）和视图（）），但是QComboBox还提供用于设置和获取项目数据的函数（例如setItemData（）和itemText（））。您还可以设置新模型和视图（使用setModel（）和setView（））。对于组合框标签中的文本和图标，具有Qt :: DisplayRole和Qt :: DecorationRole的模型中的数据用来。请注意，你不能改变的SelectionMode中的视图（），例如，通过使用的setSelectionMode（） 。
